snippet: Instead of the round-the-block lines that have greeted Apple product introductions in China and other countries in the past, only about a dozen customers showed up to buy iPhones at the opening of a store in Beijing on Friday.
abstract: Instead of the round-the-block lines that have greeted Apple product introductions in China and other countries in the past, only about a dozen customers showed up to buy iPhones at the opening of a store in Beijing on Friday.

headline.main: Daily Report: Apple's China Mobile Deal Gets Off to a Weak Start
